{"tid":680250,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一個人係關曬窗的房內，會否窒息致死","createTime":"2018-05-27T05:28:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T09:56:06.000Z","uid":154814,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4cdf0e56eeab293f769f5867009001aaa63e79e0","tid":680250,"uid":154814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:28:13.000Z","msg":"話說我新OFFICE係大廈中央冷氣，係星期六係會無冷氣，<br />\n有人話一個人係關曬窗的房內，會令腦部缺氧致死，請問係咪真, 係咪就算開風扇都無用?"},{"pid":"9bd4d6ac9baf07e9c5f129b6125b3e669a8aa096","tid":680250,"uid":57636,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:35:15.000Z","msg":"應該要睇下密封嘅空間有幾大，重有個人喺間房到做咩<br />\n間房入面嘅氧氣含量夠唔夠個人喺靜感狀況下支持到星期一<br />\n我覺得就未必可以導致窒息"},{"pid":"b6bfa1c4364b29600b1dd67372547a3cda783465","tid":680250,"uid":154814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T06:16:46.000Z","msg":"如果純粹齋坐用電腦呢?"},{"pid":"e2f7c0e5f32c0be28af2c39ad4ef5f50b7829735","tid":680250,"uid":137361,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T06:20:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f69f02dc8665c456d2b3aebc3de98fde102f4b94","tid":680250,"uid":113021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T06:38:16.000Z","msg":"照計就唔會既<br />\n因為始終有唔密實既地方<br />\n如果係中央冷氣，就算你閂埋門窗<br />\n你頭頂既風喉都會同你串通去好多地方<br />\n<br />\n不過可能會有Ｄ焗同辛苦<br />\n例如如果有太陽曬到就成個溫室咁"},{"pid":"858ec9fed0b19078ccac4fd9120c8490362d9c50","tid":680250,"uid":32219,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T07:12:41.000Z","msg":"唔想做咪辭囉<br />\n港奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4e2eb0dfc5eb4cd107040f2b68173853a3e2cca","tid":680250,"uid":90287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:47:49.000Z","msg":"有風扇能否增加氧氣?"},{"pid":"d2d4481272807b70ccf01c1a7b61ca528d7b492e","tid":680250,"uid":137361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:51:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"42417874e7d44cc66a13487ed6b613963668b0f5","tid":680250,"uid":39316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:56:06.000Z","msg":"唔會死<br />\n但會焗到好辛苦，尤其熱既時候，濕度高既話仲慘<br />\n缺氧既感覺唔太有，但會好頭痛，漸漸個人會好攰，身體好似不停催你去訓覺咁<br />\n<br />\n利申<br />\n真實經歷"}]}